comments: You can extend this section to include more of Hussie's old stuff, if you're so inclined.
Download https://github.com/MrCheeze/andrewhussie/tree/gh-pages/comics, and move its contents to [Asset Directory]/archive/tso
Then delete the entire 'list' array below, and rename 'extended_list' to 'list' so it can take its place.
The extra comics will be accessible from the tso page within the archive

list.groupDesc: A variety of casually rendered comics, spanning multiple series.

extended_list.groupDesc: A variety of casually rendered comics, spanning multiple series.
A time-honoured tradition of scribbling in books to create gifts for others.

whistles.name: Whistles: The Starlight Calliope
whistles.desc: Whistles, a clown in the Starlight Calliope circus, was beloved by all. One day an accident nearly cost him his life, and he became exposed to the corrupt underworld of the circus, rife with murder and cannibalism. Forced to flee, he experiences the hardships of the world such as homesickness and prostitution.

aids.name: And It Don't Stop
aids.desc: "Buncha years ago Andrew Hussie and I collaborated on a comic that was (even though we didn’t know it at the time) 8-Mile vs Real Steel. By collaborated, I guess I should say, I bailed way early and Andrew finished the thing like a champ." -Tauhid Bondia
